AI SAFETY RULES

Follow these exactly:

- The LLM must not calculate finance numbers.
- Use utility functions for income, expenses, net profit, overdue invoices, and revenue per follower.
- AI can only summarize already-calculated numbers.
- Every finance AI response must include the disclaimer:
  “AI insights are for informational purposes. Consult a CPA for tax advice.”
- Never fabricate synced data.
- If sync fails, show last known good value with warning text.
- Do not show zero unless the actual value is zero.

